import React from 'react'
import { Container, Row, Col } from 'react-bootstrap'


function Footer() {
    return (
     
            <footer>
                <container>
                    <Row>
                        <Col className="text-center py-3">Copyright © 2021- Laksura.com Enterprise. All right Reserved.</Col>
                    </Row> 
                </container>
            </footer>
    )
       
}

export default Footer
